const TESTIMONIALS_DATA = [
  {"name":"Jay Bansal","air":2,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image62.jpg","testimonial":"Hello friends I am Jaya bansal I secured all India rank second with a gate score of 1000 and gate computer science stream 2019. I came to know about Ravula’s sir and lecture after surfing on internet about gate 2019 and I watched some sample videos of sir and I was inspired to take all the lectures and I took took the full course of ravula Sir for two years in in 2018 in 2017 itself and I watched all the videos carefully and and take the notes of them and revised thoroughly. I recommend Ravula’s sir full lectures to everyone and my advice to Future aspirants stress Travelers are completely just as I did give as many tests as possible and tests play a key role in the gate examination. They give a complete exposure and remove the fear of the final examination."},
  {"name":"Prateek Agarwal","air":3,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image77.jpg","testimonial":"hello my name is pratik Agarwal I did B Tech from IIT kanpur I passed out in 2010. I got a all India rank of 3 in computer science gate 2019. I joined the Ravindrababu Ravula sir’s lectures two times once in 2016 and then in 2018 but it was my first attempt in Gate last time I did not give gate because of inadequate preparation and I did not attempt gate for two years now this time I gave gate and got all India rank of 3. Ravi sir's lectures are very helpful, I mean I particularly noticed previous year gate questions and video Solutions were very helpful because most of the sources were saying different things but his Solutions were coherent and gave a new perspective on those topics and I saw that he explained questions I mean in multiple times with same concept. He explained many times that helped me to clear my Concepts."},
  {"name":"Hari Shrawgi","air":6,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image29.jpg","testimonial":"Hi, my name is Hari Shrawgi and I graduated from NIT Raipur in 2008. Then I joined Broadcom and currently I am employed there also. So I secured All India Rank 6 in GATE CS exam. Like everybody else, I used to watch Ravi sir’s video for my B.Tech preparation and when I decided to pursue GATE while doing my job, I thought his videos will be the best for my preparation as I also have to do a job. So those videos really helped you to set your own pace as is not the case with class room coaching. So they are really helpful for people who are trying to do GATE while parallely working. Then coming to my preparation, I followed a very strict schedule and basically I gave a lot of tests and practiced a lot of questions. I solved all the previous year GATE questions twice. I gave around 240 tests. All thanks to Ravi Sir."},
  {"name":"Nihar Ranjan Sahoo","air":9,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image99.jpg","testimonial":"I am Nihar Ranjan Sahoo from IGIT, Sarang, Odisha. I got AIR-9 in GATE-2017. Ravindrababu Ravula sir’s lectures helped me a lot to clear all my concepts and doubts. I really appreciate sir’s effort. His motivational videos helped me to stay positive throughout my preparation. He is one of the finest teachers I have ever seen. I feel very much lucky that I got a chance to learn from him. You are doing a fabulous job sir. Keep going. `"},
  {"name":"Shivank Gupta","air":11,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image22.jpg","testimonial":"\"You are my inspiration\" since the beginning as I am pursuing my Bachelors in Electronics. Sir, you are just simply awesome and the way you had taught all subjects is more interesting. After watching videos of each subject, I hardly found any doubt and the concepts are really taught in a simple and elegant way. Along with your course videos, your motivational videos, I must say that they are a must watch for everyone and they had a great impact on me also. I used to watch them whenever I feel demotivated and off track. Thank you!"},
  {"name":"Parul Gupta","air":13,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image44.jpg","testimonial":"A few months ago while searching for Gate I stumbled upon Ravindra Sir’s demo lectures on YouTube. I watched a couple of his Networking lectures and was awed by the way he had made everything seem so simple and interesting. At that very moment I decided to opt for his full course. His knowledge, dedication and hard work reflect in his videos as they are really good in content. They help you prepare not only for GATE but also in general, develop an interest in the field of Computer Science. Thank you so much Sir. You are a motivation for millions!"},
  {"name":"Himadri Banerjee","air":15,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image71.jpg","testimonial":"I sincerely thank Ravindrababu Ravula Sir and his team for such amazing classes and explanation. His lectures and test series are the biggest reason I secured AIR 15 in GATE 2017 though I pursued my Bachelors in Electronics."},
  {"name":"Anirban Biswas","air":19,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image39.jpg","testimonial":"Tutorial videos of Ravindrababu are excellent. It really helped me understand concepts of various topics very clearly. His way of teaching is absolutely fantastic. I loved it. Videos on Computer Network and ToC were superb. Also test series was very helpful. Quality of questions were excellent."},
  {"name":"Abhishek Bhardwaj","air":20,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image11.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra Sir is an extra ordinary teacher with gifted talents and an amazing public speaker. I decided to prepare for GATE by watching his inspirational videos. I watched his free videos of all subjects on YouTube. These videos are enough for creating interest in the subjects. Moreover I also joined Ravindra Sir's test series, which contains many good questions with solution especially for computer networks and theory of computation. I learnt many concepts from test series alone. I would like to suggest any future aspirant to join Ravindra Sir's coaching and I am sure he will make you perform your best."},
  {"name":"Monish Keswani","air":21,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image89.jpg","testimonial":"My dream of getting into IISc would have remained a dream had I not come across Ravi sir's video tutorials on YouTube. The day that changed my destiny. After watching the first video itself, I was certain I wanted to watch every gate tutorial Ravi sir has ever made. He is a one man army, delivering the kind of knowledge and training no classes will ever be able to provide. The videos not only cover the breadth of the syllabus but also the depth, so it is a complete package. He has been the catalyst during my preparation whenever i felt I'm slowing down i used to watch his video \"How to get AIR 1 in GATE\" and get paced up. He is the best mentor anyone could ever ask for and no words will ever be able to express how grateful I'm. Thank you sir!"},
  {"name":"Tapan Bhardwaj","air":22,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image94.jpg","testimonial":"I have done my B.Tech in Electrical and was placed in an IT Company and wasn't sure if this is what I wanted to do in my life. Then I got to know from a friend that M.Tech in IISC CS will open different wonderful opportunities and that is how and why I wanted to give GATE. Then I came across Ravi Sir's lectures in YouTube and after watching the first couple of lectures I got to know that this is what I want to study and from whom I want to study from. The confidence that Ravi sir instills in people with even the lowest self esteem is what makes him a great guru. He lays a path for people who like to work hard and achieve things in life with his awesome lectures and motivational videos. To achieve something great you need hardwork and right path. Hard work is something that depends on your motivation but Ravi sir lectures will provide you a right path."},
  {"name":"Sunandini Sanyal","air":24,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image52.jpg","testimonial":"I would like to thank Ravindrababu Ravula Sir for my success. I watched his video lectures which helped me understand the concepts in depth. Some of his videos were truly inspiring as well. I had taken the test series which contained questions right from basic to advanced level that not only helped me analyze and learn from my mistakes but also improved my time management skills. Thanks a lot Sir!"},
  {"name":"Manish Joshi","air":28,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image102.jpg","testimonial":"Thanks to you Ravi sir for your motivational videos that made me opt GATECS and then to your lectures that made it possible, to secure AIR28."},
  {"name":"Amit Patil","air":31,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image59.jpg","testimonial":"Hello all, I am Amit Patil, from Mumbai. I studied all the subjects just from Ravindrababu Sir's video lectures, without using any standard reference books. Only his videos, practice questions and GATExcel Test Series are self-sufficient to get a good rank in GATE."},
  {"name":"Sai Prasad Koushika","air":37,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image37.jpg","testimonial":"I am Sai Prasad Kousika, I secured All India Rank 37 in GATE-2017 in Computer Science. Initially, I thought GATE was the toughest exam and it is possible to crack it only with 2 or 3 years of continuous coaching. During that time, I got to know about Ravindra sir from my seniors. They suggested me to watch his demo videos. After watching sir’s GATE introduction videos, I came to a conclusion that it(GATE) is not tough anymore. In fact, it changed my complete thought process about GATE and they taught me the way of life. That day itself I joined GATExcel 135 and practiced each and every paper. Believe me, I almost explored all concepts of the subject in depth from each question and it made me fall in love with subjects. This is what made me crack GATE in final year itself. The way sir designed and maintained that standard is Awesome. Thanks a lot sir, for making my dream come true."},
  {"name":"Kantikumar Lahoti","air":39,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image81.jpg","testimonial":"All I have achieved today, Ravindra Babu sir has a big contribution in it. Tutorials of Ravindra Babu sir were excellent. It helped me understand the concepts clearly and easily. The way he teaches is fantastic. The Test series was challenging and helped a lot in preparation. Thank you Sir for guiding me."},
  {"name":"Prerit Garg","air":42,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image66.jpg","testimonial":"I would like to thank Ravindra Babu sir for his great effort in making the videos. Once I studied a topic from his video, nothing else was required. His problem solving technique and the way of explanation without rushing the topics is what makes him different. I don't think any of the coaching institutes can ever match the effort he has put into his videos."},
  {"name":"Jatin Mittal","air":43,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image95.jpg","testimonial":"One of the best teacher I have known in my life, Mr.RavindrababuRavula Sir. He is not only a teacher but also a great inspiration. I believe it is not my achievement but that we were just means to accomplice his hardwork. I like the way he teaches, starting from the very scratch and taking the topic to the utmost level without lacking any concept at any level. He is a role model. Moreover, the only thing that matters is how badly one wants something and is there someone by his side to guide him who has already travelled through the same path. And, that guidance was well provided by Ravi Sir. May God bless every student with a teacher like him from the very beginning of his/her life."},
  {"name":"Shadab Zafar","air":59,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image31.jpg","testimonial":"The video lectures by Ravula Sir are amazing. The content is thoughtfully selected with the explanations being clear and to the point. I found the TOC lectures to be the best among the lot as the all the critical topics were covered. I owe a part of my success to these lectures and will recommend them to every serious GATE aspirant."},
  {"name":"Sudheer Chandra M","air":60,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image55.jpg","testimonial":"Ravi sir is a multi talented individual, a great motivational speaker and obviously CS genius. My Bachelors degree is in Electrical and Electronics engineering, but out of my enthusiasm towards algorithms, computer vision and AI, I decided to do Masters in CS. Ravi sir is the first person to create confidence in me from his YouTube videos that gate CS is not difficult and can be cracked with little effort. I enrolled for his classes and thoroughly enjoyed them. I loved CN, TOC and DBMS personally. Sir kept in adding motivational videos to boost confidence. Also I like sir's confidence. I see these days sir is also teaching other than gate stuff. I hope people get benefited from that also. I'm excited to share this happiness with him."},
  {"name":"Avinash Modi","air":62,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image70.jpg","testimonial":"I did my B.Tech from IIT Roorkee in Computer Science. I am currently working in Visa Inc. from last 1.5 years. I always wanted to go for higher studies. There were two options : some university in USA or IIT/IISc. Due to financial restraint, I decided to give a try to GATE. I started preparing from Ravi Sir's e-clravinasses around Mid October. His e-learnin are precise and well groomed for GATE preparation, especially for aspirants who want to secure under 100 rank. Test series provided by Ravi sir is comprehensive and cover all topics to the required depth. Test series is a must if you dont want to lose those 5-10 marks in \"THE\" exam day which could cost you severely."},
  {"name":"Ayush Lakshakar","air":62,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image110.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra sir's videos are awesome... His videos of how to keep things remember long time.. how to keep oneself self motivated during exam time, what is your reason and all other videos helped me a lot during exam time... I had very less time available for gate preparation..it is just because of his videos.. I m able to secure AIR 62 in GATE.. Thank you sir .. Thank you so much"},
  {"name":"Rahul Sharma","air":72,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image19.jpg","testimonial":"I would like to start with a big THANKS!!!! Although we were not connected physically but I always felt sir’s presence while watching the videos. I decided to prepare for GATE examination after the end of my 2nd year (B.Tech). I saw his general videos on YouTube and that inspired me to go for higher studies. I saw his demo videos of Algorithms and Computer Networks and I was satisfied with the way of teaching. Few of my college seniors too had taken up your courses so they ensured me about the quality of his teaching. I started completing all the subjects one by one and after completing a subject I practiced all the previous year GATE questions related to that subject. Once I covered the entire syllabus (85-90 percent) I started revising the subjects and towards the last months I appeared for test series that helped me to figure out my preparation. During my preparation phase I used to watch all your general videos and they always boosted my confidence. I always tried to follow the strategies that you used to tell us. You were always a part of my preparation Sir. Although all the subjects were taught superbly but here are the list of subjects that I liked most:- Computer Networks(My favourite) Operating Systems(Easiest of all) Algorithms(Entire syllabus was covered perfectly) Digital Logic(You made it look so easy, I was able to solve any type of question) TOC(The way you explained every example made it easier for me) I would like to mention the following reasons for enrolling up for your courses:I was able to watch your videos anytime as per my convinience. I was able to choose the ordering of subjects for preparation that helped me during my semester examinations too. I was able to watch all the topics as many times I wished. The course fee was reasonable as compared to other institutes."},
  {"name":"Akshay Gupta","air":75,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image111.jpg","testimonial":"Thanks’ to ravindra sir I get 75th rank in gate 2017. I prepared his leathers from last 6 months only by following the plan he explained in his videos. In the time of self-doubt, confusion and anxiety, only thing keeps me going was ravindra sir’s great guidance and his videos. Thank your sir."},
  {"name":"Ravi Shankar Karanam","air":76,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image38.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra sir has been an exemplary and visionary mentor, whom you would rarely come across. Sir, your encouragement and advice has led me to places I never thought I would go. The knowledge you have imparted to me will always remain as a great asset throughout my career. My success today is due to your support and mentorship."},
  {"name":"Shiva Kulshreshtha","air":77,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image90.jpg","testimonial":"I owe Ravindrababu Ravula sir for my success in GATE 2017. Actually I never really studied very seriously for GATE till my 7th semester, just that I prepared all the concepts from University exam and campus point of view. As I was already a fan of Ravindrababu Ravula sir by watching his YouTube videos, I decided to go for his GATE 2017 full course. This course helped me polish my knowledge from GATE point of view in some campus subjects like DSA, DBMS, etc. While it helped build up even the basics for other subjects which I hadn't even touched like CO, CD, etc. Especially the CN course I felt was unparalleled as sir has worked in Cisco and refers to latest RFC developments. Apart from the excellent technical course content, I also liked the way he took up aptitude, one thing I like about sir is that he never tell us to mug up something and explains the concepts from the basic level. Moreover, his exam tips and motivational videos were the icing on the cake, they made me believe that I can achieve my dreams, not just in GATE, but in life, and while watching the videos I felt that he genuinely cared about his students. I felt like I had found a lifelong guru and friend in sir."},
  {"name":"Rasna Goyal","air":79,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image58.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra Sir is one of the best teachers I have ever studied from. It's not what he teaches makes him so favorite ... It’s the way he teaches. Studying from him makes everything just so simple...easy&hellip;logical and interesting.... I feel so lucky to have joined his online classes. Since I started studying along with job...ease of watching anytime and anywhere helped me a lot as I could manage studying daily along with office... Without his help I don’t think it would have been possible to secure a good rank.."},
  {"name":"Anupama vijjapu","air":90,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image57.jpg","testimonial":"I came to know about Ravi Sir's lectures from a friend of mine who was preparing for GATE and this is how my journey towards cracking the exam started. He teaches with great passion from the very basic concepts of the subjects that even a B.Tech Electrical student like me can now say that I know CS much better than I ever knew Electrical. His subject lectures cover each every minute concept that could be asked in the exam. His test series are unique and cover every exceptional detail possible in the exam. His motivational videos that were released periodically few days before exams helped me a lot because they are exactly what a student wants at that point of time. So I had a great learning experience throughout the preparation time."},
  {"name":"Ashis kumar","air":96,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image24.jpg","testimonial":"The Ravindrababu Ravula. Great teacher and speaker. His motivational(general) videos are very good for someone who needs to start preparation for GATE and Computer Networks lectures are best i have seen anywhere. He is always ready to solve queries of even an unknown person."},
  {"name":"Vaishali Jhalani","air":97,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image36.jpg","testimonial":"I want to thank Ravi sir and his whole team for such wonderful classes. A big part of my success is Ravi sir’s lectures. All the lectures were somehow clearing all my doubts and it made my basics strong. Apart from concepts, exam based approach to solve every question was very helpful."},
  {"name":"Sruthi Goyal","air":109,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image106.jpg","testimonial":"Sir, THANK YOU SO MUCH. I had always been a student who could not mug up a single thing, I wanted the logical explanation behind it, and Ravi sir provided me with that. I had been following his videos since June 2016. The way he explained things- what was the problem initially and its solution and the way a certain thing came into existence- made my life a lot easier. I can't stop thanking him, especially for Computer Networks. Never in my 4 years of engineering had I understood anything about networks. Thank You Sir! Sruti Goyal Your proud student!"},
  {"name":"Shashank Pal","air":117,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image60.jpg","testimonial":"Hi friends.... I am Shashank Pal, I got Gate AIR 117 and a huge credit for this goes to Ravindra Sir. I did my B.Tech in Civil Engineering and had zero knowledge in CS but Ravindra Sir's lectures made it very easy and interesting for me. His lectures are self sufficient for gate. He has taught each and every topic in such an easy manner that anyone can understand. Apart from a great teacher, he is also a great motivator and mentor. The story that he shared about his friend who was preparing for IAS inspired me a lot. He even shared a pic of his friend. His lessons about life filled me with positivity which I needed a lot because I was being told that I won't be able to crack gate as I had civil background. He even suggested some books like \"The magic of thinking big\", \"Good to great\" which really motivated me. Thanks a lot sir without you it would have not been possible."},
  {"name":"Murali Krishna","air":119,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image50.jpg","testimonial":"My journey towards getting into one of the top IITs wouldn't be possible without your guidance sir. I had a strong motivation in life and it was your guidance that channelized it in right direction. Your e-lectures are precise for gate, complete with respect to syllabus and deep enough to thoroughly understand the concepts. I enjoyed learning. Thanks for all your effort to make concepts understandable even for below average students. I am sure your effort will bring light in millions of students life. It's an honor to have you sir ...Thank you"},
  {"name":"Nagesh","air":119,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image108.jpg","testimonial":"Hello, this is Nagesh I got AIR 119. The journey of gate started when I was in my 5th semester. I started searching what to do and while searching landed upon Ravindrababu Ravula’s video lecture. That video inspired me a lot and that was one of the factors for me to do GATE. This is my second attempt. I got 1025 rank in 2016(first attempt).But I was not satisfied. I wanted to get into top IITs. So I decided to drop an year and take up the exam next year. I had watched Ravi sir’s free video lectures before. I felt they were good, so I registered for his GATE course this time and finally got a rank of 119. Now when I look back I can tell you that it was the best decision that I made. I can proudly tell everyone that nobody has covered all the topics to the extent to which Ravindrababu sir has done. The explanations are also very good and I am proud to call myself a student of Ravindrababu sir. Thank you."},
  {"name":"Meet Sheth","air":132,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image15.jpg","testimonial":"Eclasses of Ravindrababu Ravula is one of the best source if you are a computer science student or also if you are not & if you are interested in real learning ( not exam and pointers oriented ). The best things about his teaching is the way he teaches the subject in such a beautiful manner that even after finishing long subjects like (CN , DBMS) you will feel that it’s just started and you will be eager to learn more !! If you are in CS department and you are reading this in 1st year or 2nd year , then according to me blindly register for this GATE course ( It doesn't matter whether you want to appear for GATE or not ) , you will not regret your decision. The best thing of this course is you will get very good understanding of basic core subjects of computer science only in 8-9 months of preparation which many students even don't know after completing their B.Tech.AND For GATE CS his videos sufficient, you don't need to go to any classes. Just follow his instructions and believe me you will get AIR 1 , I registered for his GATE course in 6th semester and after preparing for 9 months I got AIR 132. I didn't get AIR 1 because I didn't follow him completely but believe me He is the man which will get you to AIR 1. The test series by RAVULA is also awesome and very much relevant to GATE syllabus and for any doubts during preparation just email him and you will definitely get response. His e-classes services are just awesome. Nothing wrong in following someone who can make your journey easy and confident to reach your destination. And Gate is just an exam, don't make it a big deal."},
  {"name":"Sonu Dixit","air":136,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image8.jpg","testimonial":"Ravi Sir’s tutorial videos are excellent in terms of depth of information/concept it contains, as well as the way you have prepared them. I mean at several occasions in the duration of full course you could have skipped some concepts, but you chose to repeat the same concept again and again while solving every related question so that every student can understand the core concepts. I must say truly, this course is self-sufficient for gate aspirants. You have covered CN at extra depth. I wish I could keep them with me for my future reference. I just enjoyed watching your lectures, at times I could spend the whole day learning from your lectures. You have done a tremendous job in preparing those lectures with utmost care. Apart from Gate Lectures, your motivational talks also helped me a lot. As far as I have seen you in the lectures, you are a very nice, humble, down to earth person, with extraordinary determination (I am saying this because in one of the videos I got to know about your childhood struggles, true example of hard work always pay off). Thanks a lot Sir."},
  {"name":"Akash Rana","air":137,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image101.jpg","testimonial":"Sir’s lectures were crucial in helping me prepare for GATE 2017. It not only allowed me to make my concepts crystal clear but also provided me with nifty tricks that bumped my overall score by couple of marks easily. The video explanation for the previous year questions were super helpful. His way of teaching is awesome. And especially the way he taught Networking was too good. I can't thank him enough for my success."},
  {"name":"Vicky Agarwal","air":142,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image68.jpg","testimonial":"I'm very thankful to Ravindra Sir for providing such a quality lectures. He is the real motivating force that helped me in cracking GATE. To be honest I started preparing for GATE in October and it was his teaching which made it possible for me to get this rank in just 90 days. The best thing about his lectures is that I never found a necessity to go through standard books as his lectures have already done that for me. One last thing I would like to add is sir’s motivation is at par. It was only you who motivated me to go for GATE and kept me motivated throughout my preparations. Thank you for everything Sir!"},
  {"name":"Kalpesh Dusane","air":150,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image16.jpg","testimonial":"Sir thank you for all the guidance you have given me through your video lectures. I got to understand all theoretical concepts and most important of all is the way of solving GATE Numerical problems. This was my third attempt. You (your lectures) gave me confidence to try to solve or at least understand the numerical question which was out of my comfort zone for subjects like Computer Organization (CO). Also test series helped me revise the concepts. Sir you are my role model similar to most of the GATE aspirants. Keep up the good work."},
  {"name":"Asis Kumar Panda","air":160,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image54.jpg","testimonial":"When I saw Ravindra Sir's videos for the first time, I felt some X-factor in him which differentiates him from others. His way of looking at the problems, analyzing them and solving them helped me in my GATE preparation. Apart from studies, he also teaches lessons for life. In short, he is a complete personality. The best thing about Ravindra Sir's lectures is that he gives real time examples and co-relates the concepts with them which makes it easy for a student to understand. Ravindra Sir makes superstars from normal talent and that is his specialty. More than a teacher, he is an elder brother and guide to thousands of students like me. Thank you Sir for everything."},
  {"name":"Rajesh Koritela","air":164,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image51.jpg","testimonial":"A big Thanks to you and to your team Sir. As eclasses take very less time to prepare for the examination and with your awesome classes on Algorithms, DS and CN helped me to reach my goal very quickly and with accuracy. Once again thank you very much for your vision of online coaching and wish you all the best to take the future of youth aspirations forward."},
  {"name":"Kaushal Dubey","air":165,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image87.jpg","testimonial":"Concepts are written in books but you need someone to teach these concepts to you, that person is a Teacher. Ravindrababu Ravula sir is the best among all teachers I had ever been taught by. His language is so simple and he makes tough looking topics look extremely simple. I have been working at TCS during GATE preparation, so due to lack of time I had to study in very efficient way, his lectures turned out to be most efficient for me. Whatever he teaches is sufficient and enough for GATE. He is the hero of My JOURNEY from nowhere to AIR-165. He is not only a great teacher but also a great motivator. Thank you sir. Siddhant Bhatt : AIR-169 The advantage of Sir’s video lectures is that I can learn at my own pace, and re-watch the lectures whenever I feel the need to. GATE lectures by Ravindrababu Ravula clearly explain all concepts required for the GATE, I recommend them over classroom coaching classes. Ravindra Sir personally is very approachable and helpful."},
  {"name":"Akshat Garg","air":191,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image69.jpg","testimonial":"Hi, I'm Akshat Garg. A few months ago while searching for Gate I stumbled upon Ravindra Sir’s channel on YouTube. I watched his lectures and was awed by the way he had made everything seem so simple and interesting. As i started preparation late, i wasn't sure that i'd be able to watch all the videos so i only watched Youtube lectures and opted for his test series which was so helpful. Mocks were so much focused on actual gate. His motivational videos also helped me to stay positive throughout my preparation. I want to thank Ravindra Sir and his team for all their hardwork. Thank You!"},
  {"name":"Abhishek Uppar","air":200,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image35.jpg","testimonial":"Ravi sir’s videos are well made. In terms of their pace and content they are the best and subjects like OS, DBMS, Digital, Calculus, Computer Architecture, Computer Networks are too good. Since, I did not like all the subjects in the syllabus, your videos were really helpful in getting over them. Also your videos are useful for anybody to make notes of their own. The topics in a video are well oriented towards connecting concepts and hence help having a total idea. He knows the contents of the syllabus very well and always stick to it. But also you make it a point to always give something extra. And above all, the amount of motivation you flush through all the student minds is amazing and is much needed. India certainly needs lot more of your kind. The topics tests for some subjects are really good (like TOC, Engineering mathematics, Database, Digital Design), and they did certainly help me in clearing my doubts and concepts. The test series were useful in knowing various types of questions and managing time. The videos are really good for self paced learning and they make us feel that GATE is easily CRACKABLE (they did say the truth!).I would recommend it to anyone anytime. The videos are concise and to the point. You have a wonderful purpose which is the pursuit of serving the student with quality education online. I wish you all the best."},
  {"name":"Debanjan Ghatak","air":205,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image83.jpg","testimonial":"The e-classes of Ravindrababu Ravula helped me a lot...each and every subject and each and every topic have been covered taking care about all the minute details. The very exciting thing is that after covering each topic ravula sir takes up some previous year examples or some good questions which helps in understanding the concepts more clearly..moreover if I got stuck at any concept I mailed him the doubts and got reply within a couple of days..that’s great...his general tips about how to crack gate also motivated me a lot. Regarding test series- its filled with beautiful questions on some really good concepts...each and every test should be given with pure sincerity...it gives a good practice and trains you for the gate exam. Ravula sir is great..I wanted to get less than 100 rank but I made a couple of silly mistakes..but I would like to say anyone who watches all the videos with sincerity and takes all the tests...coming under 100 is not a difficult task. Thank you."},
  {"name":"Prateek Gupta","air":243,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image40.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra Sir has been helpful to me throughout my gate preparation. There were some problems which I came across and could not find solution anywhere on Google so just for experimentation I forwarded that problem to Sir's mail ID. And next day itself Sir and his team provided me the solution. Since then I always asked the nut cracking problems I came across and received the right answers with reasons. Also when there was any topic regarding any subject especially computer networks, I always relied upon Ravindra Sir's lectures. Not only course lectures other lectures concerning post graduate career, depression , time table for gate on YouTube helped a lot."},
  {"name":"Aman Omer","air":245,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image103.jpg","testimonial":"GATE 2017 AIR 245. All credit goes to you, Sir. Coming this far (thinking about IIT/IISc) would have never been possible without him. His way of explaining the concept is more than superb. Once again thank you very much sir. Your student, Aman Omer."},
  {"name":"Abhinav Arora","air":255,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image100.jpg","testimonial":"I would like to share my experience with Ravula Sir here. I took Ravula Sir lectures around August when I was still at my first job in a service based company. After studying simultaneously with my Job for around 2 months I decided to give full time preparation for GATE. With just 4 months of preparation from October and following Ravula Sir lectures whole heartedly I was able to crack GATE in my first attempt. He is a great teacher and a perfect motivator. I would highly recommend Ravula Sir lectures to anyone who is serious about cracking GATE."},
  {"name":"Sagar Tikore","air":283,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image20.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra Sir- Undoubtedly the best teacher I ever had..!! The best part of Ravindra sir's coaching is the Journey which has wonderful learning experience and of course a great success standing at the destination. Entire syllabus has been covered in the GATE course and I understood each and every subject with so much ease. I got my every doubt cleared within a day or two. I owe this success to wonderful teacher like you. Thank you for making a beautiful impact on my life."},
  {"name":"Ayushi Mathur","air":299,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image17.jpg","testimonial":"Hi,this is AyushiMathur and I secured rank 299 in GATE 2017 CS. And I want to THANK Ravi sir for his quality e-lectures and motivational videos. Video lectures by Ravindra sir are so helpful , especially for someone who is starting from scratch. Biggest advantage while preparing for GATE through his video lectures was the feature \"anytime & anywhere & any number of times\". He is the BEST teacher indeed! Test series provided by him was equally helpful. It helped rectifying my mistakes. Learned a lot Sir. Thank you very much & Keep up the good work."},
  {"name":"Samujjal Das","air":302,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image64.jpg","testimonial":"I consider it my proud privilege to write about you. I took your classes for GATE 2017 and got a decent rank (AIR 302). I felt that you have this amazing quality which made even the difficult topics simpler to someone having no knowledge of Computer Science. Your lectures helped me by building my base of CS subjects stronger. Thank you Sir for your support and guidance. You are awesome!!"},
  {"name":"Mohit Gupta","air":306,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image79.jpg","testimonial":"I am Mohit Gupta. I did my B.Tech in 2010 and I have a work experience of 6+ years and I got AIR 306 in GATE 2017. We can imagine how fundamentally strong an engineer from a normal college would be and that too in times when this genius called Ravindrababu Ravula hasn't made his footprints in the teaching domain. The same is the case with me. Even though a good performer in my company, I always felt inside me that I don't know my subjects well. Finally I decided to prepare for GATE just to know my subjects well and attempted GATE with 99% certainty of not leaving the Job. During my preparation I got the chance to attend TOC class in person by Ravula sir and became a fan of him and eventually registered to his videos. These remarkable lectures enlightened me about what actually computer science is and now I feel like reading more of computer science related stuffs than ever before. Though I won't be going for full time higher studies ( already married and blessed with a beautiful daughter :) ), but GATE preparation through Ravula's videos has changed my life, boosted my confidence to another level and completely changed my way of looking at things and attacking problems at my work front. I wish if Ravula would have born few years earlier and I had such quality videos in my college time. Anyways there is no age for learning and now I am applying for part-time MS from IITD. I would recommend every engineer to prepare for GATE during their college time itself as this is one of the way we get to understand our subjects well by solving previous years GATE questions which are truly conceptual and helps in solidifying the concepts learnt theoretically. I owe this new enlightenment in my dormant computer science professional carrier to Ravula sir"},
  {"name":"Preyashi Agarwal","air":312,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image26.jpg","testimonial":"I've got AIR-312 and a score of 772, I would like to thank Ravi Sir for your lectures and everything. It really helped me a lot in my preparation. I have focused on the development of concepts and practicing as many questions as possible. The test series from Ravindra sir covers the basics which is the heart of GATE. It helps building up the knowledge from understanding the basics to implementing it to various questions and scenarios. After learning basics I have focused on giving tests assuming its GATE exam and giving the GATE exam considering it another test series. Apart from this stay focused and aim high and always take motivation from your loved ones.This really help to keep a positive attitude."},
  {"name":"Ravi singh","air":316,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image86.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindrababu Ravula Sir is not only just a teacher, he is truly a complete guide for students. While coming to GATE, I had enrolled for his e-classes and test series. All the lectures were very helpful and are enough to get good understanding to crack GATE with good marks. Test series was very well scheduled and if one regularly attempts his test series which had a plenty of questions that are sufficient for practice. Thanks a lot sir &#128578;"},
  {"name":"Viral Shah","air":326,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image45.jpg","testimonial":"I started seriously preparing after mid October for Gate and sir's videos helped me to achieve my dream within a short span of time. I secured AIR-326 in GATE-2017. Ravi sir is not only just a great teacher but also a great motivator and guide. He makes things very easy and also taught about how to look at different approaches of the questions and how to tackle pressure of the examination. This may seem like exaggeration but"},
  {"name":"Shaik Masthan","air":330,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image74.jpg","testimonial":"A good teacher can teach the subject clearly but a great teacher can teach the subject clearly as well as he can teach you how to lead the life effectively Thank you RAVI sir for your amazing inspiration towards to GATE. \" ----"},
  {"name":"Srijeet Chajtterjee","air":344,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image109.jpg","testimonial":"Being a 3.5 years experienced IT professional in an MNC that too from ECE background, even thinking of cracking GATE in CS with such an opportunistic rank was unreal when I first thought of it. Then I saw some of Ravindrababu Ravula’s videos and realized, yes it can be done. The most challenging part was Automata and Compiler Design, they used to make me feel like an alien. But I have gone through his videos and that’s all, I came to know these subjects. Ravula is a fabulous teacher and I feel I’m very lucky to receive his guidance that has now put me in a position to accelerate in life and redefine it. A super thanks Mr. Ravula."},
  {"name":"Anmol maheshwari","air":344,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image6.jpg","testimonial":"This is Anmol Maheshwari. I got AIR-344 in CS branch. Well at start, I was little confused about which test series I should opt for. As there are many institutes that have this facility. I watched some guest lectures of Ravindrababu Ravula on You Tube. And they were quite amazing. So I gave it some thought and opted for GATExcel 135, a test series provided by Ravindra Babu Ravula institute. The test series was excellent. It had questions which cover almost every concept with various levels of difficulty. The solutions that were provided were accurate and still if I had any problem, I mailed them and my problem was resolved by some IITian or IIScian graduate within 24hrs. Either they would personally call me or mail me. So my overall experience was amazing. And when I gave GATE, it wasn't that hard for me. As most of the questions were repeated or had same concept. There was quite an improvement in my speed to solve the question."},
  {"name":"Rounak Agarwal","air":353,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image25.jpg","testimonial":"\"Ravi Sir's videos cover GATE syllabus quite comprehensively and they are easy to understand. The test series is also quite comprehensive. They were very beneficial to me for my GATE preparation.\""},
  {"name":"Saloni Bansal","air":374,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image3.jpg","testimonial":"I started preparing quite late and wasn't even sure whether I should go for GATE 2017 or not. But Ravi Sir encouraged me to give my best in first attempt only. His lecture videos are, no doubt, \"the best\". The simplicity with which he explained the topics made them interesting and easy to grasp on. I didn’t have time to attempt all the tests in test series and on his suggestion I took few Mock GATEs which really helped me to know what topics I had to brush up at last. But apart from that, the support you get from Ravi Sir's team with your doubts during preparation or to boost your morale when you feel demotivated is commendable. I wouldn't have done even this much if I didn't have had their support. He is not only an amazing teacher but an outstanding motivator too. Whenever I used to feel demotivated, I watch his video where he shared his story and how he overcame the difficulties and became inspiration for many. That video made me believe that nothing is impossible and that’s what I needed to believe in. He led the right path for me in the most crucial days of my preparation by telling me what to do and what not to and I am glad to have followed his advice. Sir, you have earned a great amount of respect and love from your students and you deserve every bit of it. Thank You so much., you have earned a great amount of respect and love from your students and you deserve every bit of it. Thank You so much."},
  {"name":"Shashank Shanker Khare","air":420,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image1.jpg","testimonial":"First of all, nothing can be compared to Ravula sir's dedication and approach towards making his students understand even the minute details of the subject that most students fail upon. General videos are also very helpful as they guide us the way through tough topics. A profuse collection of questions is provided in the test series to tackle with all possible questions."},
  {"name":"Vineet Puliparambil","air":427,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image21.jpg","testimonial":"Attending Ravindrababu's lectures felt more like a joyride where learning was fun. The command he had over all the subjects and the ease with which he would teach even the most difficult concepts was amazing which increased my curiosity to learn more about them. His lectures were motivating as well, which helped me especially on days when I was down. I owe my rank to Sir's teaching more than to my own hard work."},
  {"name":"Angelic Goyal","air":473,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image14.jpg","testimonial":"My rank in Gate examination is AIR 473, all Thanks to Ravindra Sir. It is said that for succeeding in such exams, include 30% of your teacher's dedication and 70% of yours, then I would say that Sir gave his 100% out of that 30% and I gave only 20% of my hard work as I never took Gate so seriously. I was one of his YouTube fan for his teaching skills, the way he gave an in depth knowledge of the CS topics starting from basics, and then I enrolled for full course out of which I watched few subject's videos. Even without completing the syllabus or revision I got a decent rank, the whole credit goes to Sir who has the capability of planting the concepts in your brain for long time through his teaching. I also practiced few tests just days before the Gate exam and in my opinion the test series is also perfect, creating exact environment like actual exam, covering all important and potential topics with proper explanation. I can't thank you enough Sir for keeping this journey of Gate preparation interesting for us through your academic as well as motivational lectures."},
  {"name":"Shivani Karnewar","air":494,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image53.jpg","testimonial":"Firstly a big thank you to Ravindra babu sir whose excellent teaching skills brought me to where I am now. Throughout my journey you were my inspiration and always will be. I would like to share my experience, before watching your videos I was not confident about cracking the GATE exam with good score but your motivation played an important role. Your way of teaching is amazing so that any ordinary student like me can understand concepts easily and clearly. Also the test series kept pushing my boundary each and every time. I am glad that I got a chance to learn from you. I will always be thankful to you for being an excellent teacher and a great motivational speaker."},
  {"name":"Abhishek Dhiman","air":510,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image63.jpg","testimonial":"The course provided by Ravula sir was very very helpful for my gate preparation. Teaching methods and video technology used is just awesome. Also there is this test series which was given free of cost to us but was worth many Rupees. All I can say is it was one of my best decisions in my life that I had purchased this course."},
  {"name":"Pramod Kumar Yadav","air":524,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image47.jpg","testimonial":"At first I tried to avoid the preparation of gate because I was not interested , but when I got to know about Ravi Sir from my senior in college, I changed my mind and joined his course. Ravindra sir has wonderful knowledge. His GATE videos are very crisp and to the point. And if you study them dedicatedly, you will surely be landing in a very good college or PSU. I saw various notes of coaching materials (hand written) and found so much abundance of unnecessary data which will never be asked in gate. But in these video data are to the point. These are few advantages that I felt after joining his course: 1. Being online classes, you can view them anywhere at any time (Especially in college). 2. Videos can be viewed unlimited number of times. 3.E-mail assistance for clarification of doubts. 4. The problem collection is another huge plus point. Especially in automata, Computer Networks, DBMS, COA are extremely helpful, almost all kinds of problems are extensively solved and discussed. 5. Test-series for testing your concepts and preparation for the exam. 6. Cost of the course is very less compared to other coaching centers. And Ravindra sir also provided motivational lectures from time to time and they kept me motivated throughout my preparation."},
  {"name":"Shefali Gupta","air":539,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image10.jpg","testimonial":"Sir I would not have been able to fetch this score with a job ,only you made it possible for me thanks alot for making concepts so clear and always motivating."},
  {"name":"Rajarshi Banerjee","air":579,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image7.jpg","testimonial":"Ludwig Van Beethoven once said - \"Don’t only practice your art, but force your way into its secrets, for it and knowledge can raise men to the divine.\" Modern society as it seems, tends to meander from this pious objective more often than not, with more and more educational and coaching institutes becoming nothing more than the former shell for what they stood for and getting reduced to mere mendacious edifices to satisfy their perverse financial agendas a good teacher is often all you need to see through this deception. Rabindrababu Ravula's lectures and videos are not only detailed but also superfluous, this man is the epitome of a teacher, and a teacher is the epitome of knowledge. It is more than enough to tediously go through all his videos to get a satisfactory rank in GATE examination."},
  {"name":"Nirav Bhavsar","air":660,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image67.jpg","testimonial":"I completely devote my success to Ravindrababu Ravula. It all started when I first watched his “What to do after B.Tech” video on YouTube. I was working in Infosys & every single word he said about service based company were 100% true and I was also feeling the same working there. So, even though I did my B.E in Electronics & Communication, it inspired me to give GATE in Computer Science and follow my interest & dream to do Master’s in IISc/IIT. He teaches every single subject from scratch so that even B.E EC student can easily understand. His way of teaching is really good & you will never feel disinterested. He first explains concepts and after that he solves lot of examples on that topic, So I never had any doubts on any topic. Only thing I can say is the amount of knowledge I gained from watching his videos is far more than the knowledge i gained from my school to college days combined. I secured AIR 660 but I feel I could have done better. I could not give my 100% in those 3 hrs and made some silly mistakes in easiest questions. But I will give GATE again next year & pursue my dream. Lastly Ravindrababu Ravula is the best teacher & mentor I have ever met."},
  {"name":"Saurabh Godse","air":746,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image32.jpg","testimonial":"I have started preparing for GATE in June 2016. At that time I haven't thought that I'll get such rank in first attempt only. So during preparation my aim was to just understand the concepts and study them in depth. Ravindrababu sir taught me all core subjects of computer science in such great manner that after completing entire syllabus my aim has changed. I have followed all the tips given by sir and that helped me a lot. Sir is just 'Legend of CSE' for me. He helped me to become a QUALITY Engineer...due to his teaching i had a good command on all the important subjects of CSE. The test series of all subjects was just excellent especially of Computer Networks. I had given all the topic tests as well as all subject tests because of which I got used to how to tackle a new problem ,how to manage time? When to leave a Q? And how you should attempt paper to score your best in any competitive examination? All subjects of computer science that I couldn't learn in 4 years, became interesting with Ravindra sir's lectures which gave me a gut feeling to be a CSE student. All the required and important topics for GATE has thorougly covered by sir at one place which saves a lot of time and makes it very easy to crack GATE. He is really a great mentor,tutor and obviously a fitness freak. Thanks a lot!!!"},
  {"name":"Amitabh Tiwari","air":957,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image96.jpg","testimonial":"\"Ravi sir is truly an amazing personality. The way he teaches and motivates to go to the extra mile is simply un parallel. It had been a year since I was working with a product based company and then thought of giving GATE for masters programme. I joined his GATE course and then it was a journey of almost 6 months of rigorous preparation. All the core subjects have been taught in a crystal clear fashion and the test series is one of the best available in market ,that has really good questions to test your grasp. I would like to dedicate my success (AIR - 957) to Ravula sir and his team.\""},
  {"name":"Shruti Jain","air":980,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image46.jpg","testimonial":"\"Joining 'GATE Lectures' by Ravindra sir was definitely one of the best decisions I have ever made. The lectures are just perfect! They cover the entire syllabus and you feel connected to them. Occasionally when you feel low, just watch some of sir’s motivational videos and you instantly get back all the enthusiasm! Apart from the excellent quality lectures, the test series is also great. The tests are perfect blend of easy and difficult questions which make you want to practice more and more. I'll always be thankful to Ravindra sir and his entire team for helping me secure a decent rank in GATE 2017.\""},
  {"name":"Avni Jain","air":983,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image61.jpg","testimonial":"Thank you Ravindrababu Ravula sir for guiding me throughout this journey of giving GATE 2017. Actually I never really studied very seriously for GATE till my 7th semester, as I was already a fan of Ravindrababu Ravula sir by watching his YouTube videos, I decided to go for his GATE 2017 full course. He made every subject so clear and easy and thanks to him I was understanding every subject rather than mugging it up ."},
  {"name":"Timojit Chatterjee","air":5,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image84.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 5 in GATE 2015 and your videos helped me. I got a good understanding of what subjects to put stress on and how to approach them. You are doing a nice job and keep going."},
  {"name":"Rishabh Singla","air":8,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image27.jpg","testimonial":"I feel very fortunate that i got opportunity to attend Ravula Sir's classes. My undergraduate college was below average and now I am studying in the best college of India. The whole credit goes to Ravula. He is more like guide than a teacher to me. GATE is about both knowledge of basic concepts in CS and confidence (which people generally lack of till exam). Ravula sir did perfect job in boosting my confidence, which eventually helped me in getting AIR 8. I wish i could attend more of his sessions for other subjects not related to GATE as well."},
  {"name":"Aman Madaan","air":null,"institution":"MTech, IITB","photo":"/testimonials/image56.jpg","testimonial":"A fantastic Teacher, Engineer and Human Being. Mr. Ravindrababu Ravula is certainly one of the best teachers I have had the good fortune of interacting with. Apart from a superb hold over the various topics across the spectrum of Computer science, he possesses excellent public speaking skills and is a true motivation mill. His classes are exuberant, and have a more session like flavour, giving students ample time to think on their own, something I feel is extremely conducive in developing a good understanding of the subject matter. (I don't remember anyone dozing off even during longest of his lectures). I know many students who started believing in themselves after attending his classes and went on to achieve goals they never thought were within their grasp. Interacting with him has always been a pleasure and I hope I will benefit from his association for days to come."},
  {"name":"Vaijenath","air":13,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image75.jpg","testimonial":"Wow!!! It feels great to write testimonial for you. 1 year before, I was reading the testimonial and thinking that they are now toppers, it’s not my thing. But after watching your free demo lectures on you tube, the way you approach the concept and your motivation I could not stop myself by enrolling at your coaching. And now after 1 year its AIR 13, that is also in the final year itself. Sir you are the only teacher of whom I watched all lectures (not skipped a single one) and some of them twice . My day used to start with your lecture and end with your smile (sometime you taught me in my dreams also). Now I will be the student of best department of best college in the India, and that is possible only because of you. Thanks a lot for changing my life. You are really a Gabbar sir, I will always be a biggest fan of you."},
  {"name":"Himanshu Pandey","air":null,"institution":"M.E. IISC","photo":"/testimonials/image76.jpg","testimonial":"GABBAR PADHATA NAHI, AAG LAGA DETA HAI.... Truly speaking, when I joined classes for GATE, I planned to get good rank so that I may get some IIT, but your motivation changed my life which inspired me to do more than getting a good rank and getting admitted in IITs. As a result I got 21st rank in GATE and joined IISc. Whenever I think of you, I am always encouraged to do something new, innovative a nd good for human beings rather than only thinking about grades and money. I found you more as a brother than just a teacher because you have not taught me only subjects rather you taught me way of life and always helped me in my all decisions. I would like to be associated with you in all phases of my life, and would like to work with you... I have a lot to say, but can't express everything in words."},
  {"name":"Akash Kanase","air":28,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image80.jpg","testimonial":"Ravi is really great teacher and motivator. His lectures on what to do on 2 months before the exam, 40 days before the exam ,30 days before the exam and how to attempt the exam were useful. HIs lectures on Keep yourself motivated motivated me, every time I felt tired and bored and wanted to stop preparation. His video about Taking The Breaks is very important to every aspirant considering if I had followed it I might have not faced back pain issue I have faced. He has always been health conscious and used to take care of health of his student.I remember when he used to teach for us in classroom coaching if he felt that even single student is tired / sleepy he used used to ask all students to stand up and made us do quick workout. His lectures are really good quality and he has made preparation easy for first time preparing students. His lectures on difficult subjects like Operating systems, Computer Networks etc. makes that subject really easy. You are doing a Great job and keep doing."},
  {"name":"Pijush Chakraborty","air":28,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image30.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 28 in GATE 2015 with just 4 months of preparation using your videos.Thank you for helping students like us with the Gate preparation. I have watched all your videos and the videos are excellent. I got to learn a lot of new things.."},
  {"name":"Chiranjeev Kumar","air":47,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image5.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 47 in GATE 2015 with just 4 moths of your coaching. I was placed in Samsung Research Noida, in my campus placement. But after joining Samsung, I again got frustrated, as the work quality there doesn't even match their name. So I was continuously searching on youtube and google, what to do and what not to do. In the process I found your video lectures on youtube. I watched all the compiler design lectures in one go and realized that I need such guru. and contacted you and got myself enrolled in the full video course. I must say, I thoroughly enjoyed all the lectures. It's because of those lectures that I got 70.16 marks in Gate-2015 and AIR-47. My first two digit AIR. I even switched my company and joined Adobe-Noida. Sir, I'm greatly fascinated by Science and Technology and this time influenced by you as well, want to be a researcher in future."},
  {"name":"Rajeev Kumar Gautam","air":null,"institution":"IIT Bombay","photo":"/testimonials/image12.jpg","testimonial":"I learn a lot in teaching and apart from teaching i also learn practical aspect of study"},
  {"name":"Nirmal Kumar Boran","air":null,"institution":"IIT Delhi","photo":"/testimonials/image97.jpg","testimonial":"Thank you for being the guiding lighthouse in this ocean of information and leading us all to the shores of knowledge and wisdom Everyday we have felt Iove of God in your interactions with us be it the classroom or personal lives. You are among those very few guys in my life whom I can give credit of getting into IIT. I still remember each and every statement of you and follow all your posts ,statements . I still remember your statement which is more about life 'If there is nothing worth dying for, there is nothing worth living for' You are true GURUKUL teacher !! Thank you for your efforts in serving the Lord. May God continue to bless those efforts. I would like to dedicate Kabirs ji's doha to you : Even if the whole earth is transformed into paper with all the bigtrees made into papers and if the entire water in the seven oceans are transformed into writing ink, even then the glories of you cannot be written. So much is your greatness. Guru govind dou khade kake lagu pau! Bali hari guru aapne govind diyo batay!!"},
  {"name":"Amani Kongara","air":null,"institution":"IIIT D","photo":"/testimonials/image18.jpg","testimonial":"Hello folks! I am Amani Kongara, from Andhra Pradesh, doing my Masters at IIIT, Delhi. During my Bachelors, I got used to the standards there and never thought out of that. On the course of preparing for GATE, I joined the institute started by Ravindra Babu Ravula, where I found the life. After joining his institute, with in no time all of our friends realised how fun the learning is. It is there where I learnt everything in the correct way. It is there where we got to know that acquiring knowledge is not just learning Computer Science. Finally it is where I found myself and built my attitude. I owe him a lot because it is because of him that I am happy for what I am today..."},
  {"name":"Nirmalendu Diwakar","air":null,"institution":"IISC","photo":"/testimonials/image98.jpg","testimonial":"Marking the most important day in my life. Got admission call from IISc ME in CSE. Received the mail at 06:43 p.m. have been thinking that its a dream. All because of the greatest instructor in CS Sir Ravindra Babu Ravula. Would be thankful to you always.."},
  {"name":"Suraj Kaushal","air":null,"institution":"ME, IISc","photo":"/testimonials/image91.jpg","testimonial":"I thank Ravula Sir for making the toughest topics of TOC,Networks & other subjects so easy to understand,for which u don't need any prior knowledge about the subject bcoz he starts with the basics & goes to maximum level of GATE.It helped me a lot & would be beneficial to anyone preparing for GATE to get a good rank.I strongly recommend to watch his videos. If u are willing to be in the top rankers"},
  {"name":"Suvita Phulia","air":null,"institution":"ME, IISc","photo":"/testimonials/image43.jpg","testimonial":"It started when I joined Gate coaching with the hopes of clearing GATE exam. I wasn't able to pull up studies due to lack of motivation.Then, Gabbar Sir started taking classes. His classes were very interesting and his talks were very inspiring. He guided us towards the correct targets. I started enjoying studies and my subjects. He mainly used to focus on concepts of the courses. My performance increased drastically and I was able to get decent rank in GATE exam. I took admission in Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore. Now, I am placed in Citrix R&D Pvt. Ltd. The credits of my journey and my merits goes solely to him. It was a great opportunity to be under his guidance. He is a true mentor. Thank You Sir. (#Respect)"},
  {"name":"Astha Jada","air":51,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image28.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 51 in GATE 2015. I started attending his classes just 4 months before the exam. Ravindra Sir is a professor that inspired me from his first lecture. His teaching style is praiseworthy and he always makes sure everyone gets every single topic. His motivational words were also the key factor for my AIR."},
  {"name":"Sneha Sinha","air":52,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image105.jpg","testimonial":"I am Sneha Sinha in my final year CSE, NIT Rourkela.My gate AIR is 52 in GATE 2015 and I have followed your lectures for just 4 month.I am very grateful to you for providing so many videos which cleared all my doubts."},
  {"name":"Vikrant Singh","air":56,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image33.jpg","testimonial":"I started Ravindra sir's classes just 4 months before the exam and I got an AIR 56 in GATE 2014. I really want to thank him for his classes that helped me get this."},
  {"name":"Naga Raj","air":70,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image88.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 70 in GATE 2015. I just attended your classes, read the notes and gave the exam. I didn't read anything else. All the questions I attempted were from your notes and I got everything right. Thank you sir."},
  {"name":"Shivani Agarwal","air":71,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image107.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 70 in GATE 2015. I just attended your classes, read the notes and gave the exam. I didn't read anything else. All the questions I attempted were from your notes and I got everything right. Thank you sir."},
  {"name":"Aakash Chaudhary","air":73,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image93.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 73 in GATE 2015 and thanks to you for your lectures. They have helped me to get this."},
  {"name":"Ajay Agrawal","air":82,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image4.jpg","testimonial":"Not only the best teacher I have got till today but also a very good motivational speaker. He makes the topic so much easy to understand that you can never forget it. Got AIR 82 in GATE 2016 under his guidance. Thanks a lot, Ravi sir"},
  {"name":"Ajay Singh","air":96,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image34.jpg","testimonial":"I got AIR 96 in GATE 2015 by taking your online classes. Thank you sir"},
  {"name":"Peyush Sopori","air":null,"institution":"ME, IISc","photo":"/testimonials/image73.jpg","testimonial":"I'm one your students whom you taught for GATE. I'm really grateful for your help and great teaching during my preparation.I have been given admission to ME course at IISC, and have decided to take admission here only. Peyush sopori (ME, IISc"},
  {"name":"Ratnakar Bollu","air":null,"institution":"IIT MADRAS","photo":"/testimonials/image85.jpg","testimonial":"Hello everyone,If you have any doubt in the phrase,'All power is with in you,you can do anything and everything', Ravindra sir will explain and made you to believe that you actually had.That true words gave me courage and confidence to score in gate even after getting job and even after 2 failed attempts in GATE. Thank you Ravindra sir"},
  {"name":"Pranjul","air":null,"institution":"Mtech (IIT Kanpur","photo":"/testimonials/image23.jpg","testimonial":"Finally MY journey ended with IIT KANPUR . Learned a lot and very very special thanks to my GURU Mr Ravindra babu Ravula . Apart from my 9 hour job , his online lectures really proved to be very helpful in converting the call . Getting a good rank in gate is easy but real competetion lies in converting the call where u have to be the best among the best. Most of the coaching centres dont really taught subjects keeping in mind the interviews at iit's but This man is technical god who came into my life at a very crucial moment and leave no stone unturned in his teachings to make concepts crystal clear. :)"},
  {"name":"Balender Kumar","air":null,"institution":"IIT KANPUR","photo":"/testimonials/image2.jpg","testimonial":"Today whatever i m just because of u sir i want to touch your feet once . when i do this i feel like that i m in the heaven .sir i tell ur story to my parents they always blessing u sir...my parents proud on me but sir i think i m not able to do this without your inspiration."},
  {"name":"Chandan Pandey","air":null,"institution":"MTech, IIT kanpur","photo":"/testimonials/image48.jpg","testimonial":"I remember when i first saw your videos on youtube. These videos inspired me to take Gate 2015 seriously and I learned a lot from you after registering for your full course. The best thing is I changed my approach of analysing concepts and solving problems. As a result I got M Tech Admission in IIT Kanpur. Thank you sir for teaching and inspiring Shivam Maheshwari : ( AIR 176 - GATE 2016) From blessings of my parents and your motivational and lecture videos .I got AIR 176 in gate 2016 and going to join IIT kharagpur . Thank You so much sir for such inspirational videos . Your videos of CN , ADA , compilers , DBMS and OS helped me a lot in GATE as well as in my academics. video : 'what is your reason' will always motivate me to do more for my parents. I opted your method of revising notes and It really worked for me. Thank you so much. I wish I could meet you once in my life ."},
  {"name":"Sandeep Kumar","air":null,"institution":"Google","photo":"/testimonials/image72.jpg","testimonial":"I am working with Google India for the past one year. But I must say that this is the right platform where we can study core subject of computer science like algo, data structure, computer network etc. In totally different way. Videos are self sufficient to clear any competitive exam like Amazon, flip-kart, Cisco etc. It open a door into the real world of IT industry. Let's make our dream to come true with the help of this platforms. Sir you are doing good job in this field. Best of luck."},
  {"name":"Ashraf Ali Shaik","air":null,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image65.jpg","testimonial":"I was a confused ECE Graduate Student who has intention to learn but never figured out a way to learn CS. After Watching your videos, I know how to learn, I know to look exactly for the main point and cut out all the crap. Able to learn any tool or language or technology using the basics from Algo,Networks,OS,DBMS. Able to code optimally by designing my own Algorithm for any given problem. Connect to any remote servers & clients and use any protocol from command line across subnets. I can easily write multithreaded programs and can easily synchronize them. I can explain Normalization even if some one wakes me up in middle of my sleep. I can actually visualize recursion . (I think it would have taken 3 to 4 years for me to understand this). GPA in Sem 3 -- 3.85/4 ---- Sem 4 -- 4/4. I have confidence in me that i can clear interview rounds more easily.I have dedicated just 3 months of my time to just watch your videos and i was able to clearly see the difference in my confidence. I was able to answer a lot of questions from basics and i was able to guess what they will be asking next.I don't know about GATE but the precision with which you explain each concept is brilliant. Thanks a lot for helping me and i am pretty confident that these qualities taught by you will give me an edge over other people in my professional life. I have got an offer as Associate software developer from Pearson Education and i am joining my job from Monday."},
  {"name":"Sanket Mishra","air":null,"institution":"Phd","photo":"/testimonials/image42.jpg","testimonial":"Words fail me when I have to write something about you. It had been a wholesome experience to learn anything from you,the subjects vary and the depth of your knowledge is clearly envisioned in them increasing exponentially with each lecture. I am now PHD scholar at BITS Pilani Hyderabad Campus only by the way you guided me to reach my goals. In comparison to the commercialised coaching of other institutes, you put stress wherever necessary rather than throwing unnecessary weights on unnecessary topics.. Most beautiful and amazing lectures of ToC, Discrete Maths, Algorithms and Databases were instrumental in helping me get a different perspective on these subjects and gaining firm foothold on them. The questions that followed tested one's ability and analytical thinking that can successfully refine the learning process.. last but not the least the words of motivation proved fruitful at right hours when the stress was at its peak. I knew something but you helped me learn how to get to that point and honestly, noone of present day coaching in Gate are as good as yours.. the elucidation,the spontaneity,the magnanimity,the humbleness go in tandem with the rich repository of knowledge and awesome eloquence skills you possess.. I dedicate my success to you sir as my perseverance coupled with your guidance helped me find directions in life and I will borrow your help whenever I feel I lose my path."},
  {"name":"Dhananjay Vashistha","air":null,"institution":"CISCO","photo":"/testimonials/image9.jpg","testimonial":"Thank you so much for teaching these GATE courses so nicely, especially Computer Networks. Your Computer Network Lectures helped me so much. Just now, I got placed in CISCO as a Network Consultant Engineer(NCE) in Bangalore with 12 LPA. I did 6 months thesis last year in Network Security. I just followed your lectures blindly & the result is: I've sent my work for a European Journal for publication. I am attaching first two pages of my thesis report with this mail. Please, read the second paragraph of Acknowledgement. How can I miss my loving teacher Ravindra Sir in Acknowledgement. I am telling about these two things: CISCO placement & Thesis work not to show off, but I just want to thank you with the core of my heart for touching my life through your video lectures. At some point of time in life, I would like to touch your feet. You are my Guru who helped me so much. I think, this email of mine might have given you joy and satisfaction."},
  {"name":"Akshay Jindal","air":null,"institution":"Aircent","photo":"/testimonials/image49.jpg","testimonial":"Hello Ravi Sir, Today I got placed at Aricent. Its a networking company.After written Faced 1 hour interview all questions on Computer Networks with a little bit of DS(all easy), and I can say that I nailed the interview (literally) all because of you. The bigger picture in mind is still GATE 2014. While interview I was explaining like a pro to him, and the interviewer was very happy with me. Seriously blessed to be your student sir. May your fan following break all records. Live Long and Prosper Gabbar"},
  {"name":"Pradeep Kumar","air":null,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image41.jpg","testimonial":"Ravindra babu ravula, is the name when it just come to my mind, I get charged with the power of 440Watt. Dear Sir, you are the person who taught me and many of other people who came in contact with you, the way how to live a great life with good moral values. I met with many good teachers in my life but you are the one to whom I can call the great teacher(THE MASTER). Many people in this world you find advising others to do some good but they don’t tell how to do it, when do it and if any obstacle come in the way how to overcome but Sir you gave me each answer and cleared all doubts which stop a person to star his/her pursuit. I feel honored that I met you, got a chance to learn things from you. Its been complete one year and still I feel the line you said on the first day we met “If there is nothing worth you can die for, there is nothing worth you can live for”. You teach everything about life aim, education, ethics, love . I never saw a person with so much energy. I heard about the Dalai Lama that when He goes through somewhere a kind of positive energy flows in that place, I don’t feel less than that about you. You are always ready to help people. You are a good friend and a great Master. I can write a book on you that kind of person you are and surely I am gonna do this. Last but not the least all can say is that” you are a game changer “. Guys I can bet with you on the first day you will become fan. The way of teaching and listening to the problems of everyone and taking steps to change society and always motivating people to do so makes you an extraordinary man. I hearty feel that I am so lucky that I got a Master like you in my life. Thanx for being a true friend and master,,,J:- Pradeep Pannu, Thapar University."},
  {"name":"Rajneesh Pareek","air":null,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image13.jpg","testimonial":"I have been studying from your online lectures and got gate qualified in 2015.Thank you for providing such a greatguidance and motivation at right time.I have been selected in PhD. programme in mnnit allahabad which was my ultimate goal when i started taking your lectures.I also applied in certain college as a faculty and got good score there too.Thanks for all above."},
  {"name":"Bhavan Kumar","air":null,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image92.jpg","testimonial":"I am Bhavankumar..I am from a local college from karnataka CS&E dept. I got failed in second semister of engineering. My result was full low. One fine day, I saw MY GURU RAVI sir on youtube. Then my life started. He is god of computer science, the way he teaches, even a small guy can understand it. Even after having less result, I got into a dream company just because of Ravi sir. I took online coaching from sir. I got placed in 2 companies Tecnotree(core) and Oracle(dream). Now i am working in oracle as a application developer just because of him. I started following what ever he used to tell me. I took a scan copy of his photo and pasted in my room, daily i used to see him and get inspired. Now he became a part of my life. Still i didn't get a chance to meet him. I dedicate my success to him. He is my god."},
  {"name":"Ashmitha Singh","air":null,"institution":null,"photo":"/testimonials/image82.jpg","testimonial":"Ravi Sir, well, a lot to tell about him- He is an awesome lecturer who sentences concepts in an easy way so as to make his students feel interesting about the subject. His class will never be boring because he just not goofs up wid theory, rather teaches u in an practical manner. We always feel that he is one among us who is teaching .We eagerly wait for his next class,such an enthusiastic person he is. He is very illuminative and spends his most of the time with students. Desire, Believe and Enjoy is his mantra. Rather than a Lecturer, we find him as our IDOL and follow him. If you have any problem, he is always there for u. Apart from all these, He is very handsome :D He is complete amass of a perfect person :) Thats why, we all love and respect him.ThankYou sir for everything. Whatever I am till now, I owe to u."}
];

// Sorted: AIR ranks ascending first, then institution/no-rank entries at the end
export const testimonials = [...TESTIMONIALS_DATA].sort((a, b) => {
  if (a.air != null && b.air != null) return a.air - b.air;
  if (a.air != null) return -1;
  if (b.air != null) return 1;
  return 0;
});
export default testimonials;
